contentPageHeader.title: Publications
contentPageHeader.summary: The list of publications available are posted here. They include an information booklet on Singapore's Free Trade Agreements and Digital Economy Agreements, Future Tense - which covers emerging issues that could transform Singapore's economy, as well as economic plans or reports such as the Report of the Committee on the Future Economy.
